## About turkey-address-api

This is a web api that helps you to find addresses in Turkey.
- Simple, fast.
- Provides pagination(only streets)
- [Demo](http://tr-dr.kayaserhat.com)

## Run on development mode
- `composer install`
- `php artisan serve`

## Migrate db with .sql file
- `php artisan db:seed`
